wpantund[253126]: NCP => [INFO]-CORE----: Non-volatile: ... pid:0x49242ee0, mlecntr:0x32f8, maccntr:0x32c8, mliid:f3fead611eecae7d}
wpantund[253126]: NCP => [INFO]-CORE----: Non-volatile: Removed ChildInfo {rloc:0x5c02, extaddr:4e1185c08ce7183e, timeout:240, mode:0x05}
